platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: La galaxie a besoin de vous!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Thanks, space crooks! Because of you, were back in the saddle, enforcing the law in one of our favourite wild-west futures. Like last time, the gorgeous, open-ended levels do a stellar job of rewarding stealthy tactics and in-your-face gunplayyour choice. Whether we snuck or shot our way through enemy hideouts, we had a blast.
